	"darkforce manipulation" => "<p>XcharnameX can generate and control the extra-dimensional energy-form known as &#34;Darkforce.&#34;This resembles a tangible, impenetrable shadow and possesses several unique characteristics that XcharnameX can use to develop Power Stunts:
