	"energy absorption" => "<p>XcharnameX can absorb any form of energy, whether natural or Power-based, and not suffer any damage. XcharnameX can absorb energy equal to XcharnameX Power rank number. This stored energy can be released at any time he desires; upon release it has a lower Intensity than its original state (-2 Ranks). XcharnameX may also choose to harmlessly dissipate the energy over a long period; this is a number of minutes times ten equal to the Intensity (rank number) of the absorbed energy.
