	"Energy Sponge" => "<p>XcharnameX can absorb any form of energy, whether natural or Power-based, and not suffer any damage. XcharnameX can absorb energy equal to XcharnameX Power Rank Number.
</p><p>
	This stored energy can be released at any time XcharnameX desires; upon release it has a lower Intensity than its original state (-2CS). XcharnameX may also choose to harmlessly dissipate the energy over a long period; this is a number of turns equal to the Intensity rank number.
</p><p>
