	The second possibility is that a &#34;gag refle XcharnameX &#34;takes effect. Just as a human e XcharnameX pels all food when the intake limit is reached, so too will XcharnameX simply, uncontrollably release all absorbed energy at once. This situation assumes XcharnameX doesn&#039;t know XcharnameX own limit, or has a low Intuition (Typical or lower).
